{"tid":2065286,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Super Mario Maker 2 涉辱華全中國下架　又因自由玩法「惹出禍」","createTime":"2020-06-15T12:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T13:27:25.000Z","uid":141060,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4140d7b2c82645a27e9075876733a594aa5dbf45","tid":2065286,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死人<br />\n繼續一堆只識怪遊戲太自由既九菜怒屌遊戲公司~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200615/349189549970296832.jpeg/Fr3xH_quRphMRrU-xBrWaB2X_eadfn3-gXjoaYF46Gk?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200615%2F349189549970296832.jpeg%2FFr3xH_quRphMRrU-xBrWaB2X_eadfn3-gXjoaYF46Gk%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=ee3232e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Super Mario Maker 2 涉辱華 中國下架】近年中國對遊戲的打擊越趨猛烈，除收緊遊戲審核的標準，連水貨遊戲的市面都受到明顯影響。大熱的《動物之森》日前就因為遊戲內出現涉及政治和疫情的圖片，突然在中國各大網上購物渠道下架。這個浪潮現已沖到《Super Mario Maker 2》（超級瑪利歐創作家2）身上，沒想到這隻創作 Mario 關卡的遊戲，也同樣因為「太自由」被中國封殺。<br />\n<br />\n《Super Mario Maker 2》<br />\n<br />\n《Super Mario》可能是不太熱愛遊戲的人，也會接觸過的超大熱遊戲，Nintendo 甚至提供機會，讓玩家可以自行創作獨一無二的關卡。《Super Mario Maker 2》在 Switch 上更是進一步提供大量的素材，如果上 Youtube 搜尋玩家的設計，大多數會找到通關率極低的變態關卡。而《Super Mario Maker 2》在中國突然下架的原因，就正正和遊戲內可以自由創作關卡有關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200615/349188319818682368.jpeg/7ZPKdGWPvVR43sdYLsMeHnVTMjlVWOSye3TbN3t02zc?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200615%2F349188319818682368.jpeg%2F7ZPKdGWPvVR43sdYLsMeHnVTMjlVWOSye3TbN3t02zc%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=759310ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200615/349188819720998912.jpeg/CwZJEBeJTwQW3sSbrbIhO-_VVJTVGp80JsJeSCbCXkg?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200615%2F349188819720998912.jpeg%2FCwZJEBeJTwQW3sSbrbIhO-_VVJTVGp80JsJeSCbCXkg%3Fv%3Dw800&h=907f07bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再一次太自由出事<br />\n<br />\n由於中國國行的 Switch 遊戲，只有 3 隻能通過審批推出（《Mariokart 8 Deluxe》﹑《Super Mario Odyssey》﹑《Super Mario Bros.U Deluxe》），因此《Super Mario Maker 2》在中國只能購買水貨遊戲。有玩家就發現，在中國各個網購平台突然找不到《Super Mario Maker 2》，經網民討論後發現或如《動物之森》被禁原因類似，自由玩家涉及政治和諷刺成份。<br />\n<br />\n《Super Mario Maker 2》的玩家創作關卡中，發現有部分關卡名有諷刺成分，如「朱明錦衣衛，大清文字獄，不及振梁家貴族禁評」，甚至用戶名稱用上「8964」，因此這遊戲就突然在網購平台消失。當然，已購買的遊戲仍可以遊玩，仲要再入手就非常困難，照這種一涉及敏感內容就「被消失」的情況，中國玩家將來可能要玩水貨遊戲也不容易。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200615/349188719762345984.jpeg/Y1-qlMWNOT8NQ60zDTsMlQW1KgccBGkiJ2M3SSdjN0k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200615%2F349188719762345984.jpeg%2FY1-qlMWNOT8NQ60zDTsMlQW1KgccBGkiJ2M3SSdjN0k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fd37fcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200615/349188724522881024.jpeg/F08TWSXfaaZXMQiF0rI21XVQp72KbBe6bD8P9Ww_D_U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200615%2F349188724522881024.jpeg%2FF08TWSXfaaZXMQiF0rI21XVQp72KbBe6bD8P9Ww_D_U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e99e794b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51b912cacdfbd868d8dcb1d91f7cbb708546b2e7","tid":2065286,"uid":76848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4140d7b2c82645a27e9075876733a594aa5dbf45","tid":2065286,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:33:15.000